text: (eyaṭa) mūsā tama janatāvaṭa “oba allāh vetin udav upakāra illā (firavungen obaṭa æti vana duk gæhæṭa) ivasā darā ganu. niyata vaśayenma mema bhūmiya allāhṭama ayitiya!meya tama vahalūngen taman adahas karana ayaṭa ayiti kara denu æta. (hon̆da) avasānaya (allāhṭa) biya vannanṭaya” yayi pævasuvēya
